data.text: 1/3 Prince Arthur, the Duke of Connaught, son of Queen Victoria, was one of the present Queen's godfathers in 1926. She returned the favour 22 years later by including his name in those of her firstborn: Charles Philip Arthur George.

1/2 These the three figures from whom Prince Louis Arthur Charles got his name: 
Lord Louis Mountbatten
Prince Arthur, Duke of Connaught
Prince Charles, Prince of Wales
